docs.description: The Zillow Home Rental Index is Zillow's estimate of the median rental price of all homes within the state of Connecticut. This is derived by taking the estimated rent price for each home and dividing it by the homes square footage. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.

sources.description: Zillow is an online real estate database that was founded in 2005 and created by Rich Barton and Lloyd Frink, former Microsoft executives and founders of Microsoft spin-off Expedia. Spencer Rascoff is the current CEO of Zillow, Inc.
